{
  "stem": "11144.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess they probably-- either some neighbors discovered that they were having a Jewish girl, because that was happening quite often, or they heard maybe the Germans were coming, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they send me-- they send me back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, my sister, on the other hand-- my mother again found some-- found some Poles or Ukrainians, too, and again developed a relationship with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took my sister in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, OK, they are going to tell the neighbors that she's a cousin who came-- whose parents passed away, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she came to live with them from whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My sister was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was with them for maybe a couple of weeks or a month.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she developed sickness that you get like-- it's contagious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know how it's in English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very contagious and it's very-- it's like pimples all over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know-- and it was infectious disease, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so when they disc-- when they found that-- when they found that she was sick, they somehow got in touch with my mother.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told my mother to take her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother went and picked her up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was walking through the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of the southern, a German comes over to her and says, [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my sister, at that moment, says, 'Mama.' When they heard that she spoke Polish, they let them go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was one of very close calls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe my mother did come and visit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe I got some food from them and I passed on to my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is possible, but I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, children didn't have their own rooms there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
